issue.title: IOT platforms planning and prototyping
issue.body:
Platform candidates:
* Google Glass (Have)
* Pebble Smartwatch (MISC) (CloudPebble/RebelOS) (Have)
* Myo Armband (Have)
* Arduino (MISC) (Have)
* Raspberry PI (MISC) (Have)
* [Gadgetbridge Supported Devices](https://f-droid.org/en/packages/nodomain.freeyourgadget.gadgetbridge/) (I don't have these):
  * Pebble, Pebble Steel, Pebble Time, Pebble Time Steel, Pebble Time Round [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Pebble)
  * Pebble 2 [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Pebble)
  * Mi Band, Mi Band 1A, Mi Band 1S [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Mi-Band)
  * Mi Band 2 [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Mi-Band-2)
  * Amazfit Bip [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Amazfit-Bip)
  * Amazfit Cor (no maintainer) [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/Amazfit-Cor)
  * HPlus Devices (e.g. ZeBand) [Wiki](https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/wiki/HPlus)
  * Teclast H10, H30 (WIP)
  * NO.1 F1 (WIP)
  * Liveview
  * Vibratissimo (experimental)
  * XWatch (Affordable Chinese Casio-like smartwatches)

issue.title: Localize NLP**
issue.body:
### \*\*NLP Implementation - To be localized and FLOSS, candidates:
* Mozilla Deepspeech (Tensorflow[py] based)(Language Model: KenLM)(Mozilla Public License 2.0)
* Facebook AI Research Automatic Speech Recognition Toolkit (wav2letter)(LUA based)(Language Model: KenLM)(BSD Licensed)
* Kaldi Speech Recognition Toolkit (C++)(Apache 2.0 License)
